    <chapter id="what-is-daylight-cycle" title="What is daylight cycle?">
        <p>
            In <emphasis>Kimetsu no Yaiba</emphasis> universe, demons and humans cannot encounter except during the
            night.
            It becomes a problem when it comes to make a game where players can choose between demon and slayer ;
            and when they have to encounter each other.
        </p>
        <p>
            To solve this problem, we set the daylight cycle mechanic.
            How it works?
            The daylight system decomposes itself in two versions: <control>solo</control> and
            <control>multiplayer</control>.
        </p>
    </chapter>

