    <chapter id="daylight-multiplayer-version" title="Multiplayer version of the daylight cycle">
        <p>
            The multiplayer map has its own daylight cycle system.
            This system is similar to the real-life one, but at a faster scale.
        </p>
        <p>
            The scale is <control>1:3</control>.
            In-game, the time passes <control>3 times faster</control>.
        </p>
        <p>
            Since demons and humans are mixed in the map, the benefits of each race are the same as in the
            <control><a href="#daylight-solo-version">Solo version</a></control>.
        </p>
    </chapter>
